Alert

Version 1.2 (24 Feb '94)

N.B.	The widget files are computer-generated. The real source is
	*.w. It has been processed with Wbuild (available by
	anonymous ftp from ftp.let.rug.nl)

Author:	Bert Bos <bert@let.rug.nl>
	Alfa-informatica, Rijksuniversiteit Groningen, The Netherlands

History
1.0	April 1993
1.0.1	Replaced ltoa() with sprintf(), which seems more portable
1.1	[Dec 93] Added Converters.h and installed String->Icon converter
1.2	[Feb 94] Changed computation of initial geometry.
	Now copies $buttons to local string, before strtok() changes it.
	Uses nested RowCols instead of Board, for easier layout.

